[
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " This is the prophetic message that the "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "Lord"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " gave to"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Micah of Moresheth. He delivered this message"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " during the reigns of"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Jotham, Ahaz, and Hezekiah, kings of Judah. The prophecies pertain to"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Samaria"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " and Jerusalem."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Listen, all you nations!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Pay attention, all inhabitants of earth!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "The sovereign "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "Lord"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " will testify"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " against you;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "Lord"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " will accuse you"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " from his majestic palace."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "  "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Look,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " the "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "Lord"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " is coming out of his dwelling place!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "He will descend and march on the earth’s mountaintops!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " The mountains will disintegrate"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " beneath him,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and the valleys will be split in two."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "The mountains will melt"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " like wax in a fire,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the rocks will slide down like water cascading down a steep slope."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " All this is because of Jacob’s rebellion"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " the sins of the nation"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " of Israel."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "How has Jacob rebelled, you ask?"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Samaria epitomizes their rebellion!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Where are Judah’s pagan worship centers, you ask?"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "They are right in Jerusalem!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " “I will turn Samaria"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " into a heap of ruins in an open field – "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "vineyards will be planted there!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "I will tumble"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " the rubble of her stone walls"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " down into the valley,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and tear down her fortifications to their foundations."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " All her carved idols will be smashed to pieces;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "all her metal cult statues will be destroyed by fire."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "I will make a waste heap"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " of all her images."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Since"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " she gathered the metal"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " as a prostitute collects her wages,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the idols will become a prostitute’s wages again.”"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " For this reason I"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " will mourn and wail;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "I will walk around barefoot"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " and without my outer garments."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "I will howl"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " like a wild dog,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and screech"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " like an owl."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " For Samaria’s"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " disease"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " is incurable."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "It has infected"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Judah;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "it has spread to"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " the leadership"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " of my people"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and has even contaminated Jerusalem!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Don’t spread the news in Gath!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Don’t shed even a single tear!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "In Beth Leaphrah sit in the dust!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Residents"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " of Shaphir,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " pass by in nakedness and humiliation!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "The residents of Zaanan can’t leave their city."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Beth Ezel"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " mourns,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "“He takes from you what he desires.”"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Indeed, the residents of Maroth"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " hope for something good to happen,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "though the "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "Lord"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " has sent disaster against the city of Jerusalem."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Residents of Lachish,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " hitch the horses to the chariots!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "You"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " influenced Daughter Zion"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " to sin,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "for Israel’s rebellious deeds can be traced back"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " to you!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Therefore you"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " will have to say farewell"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " to Moresheth Gath."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "The residents"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " of Achzib"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " will be as disappointing"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "as a dried up well"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " to the kings of Israel."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Residents of Mareshah,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " a conqueror will attack you,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the leaders of Israel shall flee to Adullam."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Shave your heads bald as you mourn for the children you love;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "shave your foreheads as bald"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " as an eagle,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "  "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "for they are taken from you into exile. "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  }
]